description: Flutter widget, model, and theme conventions
globs: baller_app/lib/**/*.dart
alwaysApply: false
---

## Widget structure

- Prefer `StatefulWidget` + private `State` for data-bound UI; load async work in `initState`.
- Async shell: `baller_app/lib/auth/auth_gate.dart` (loading / error / empty branches).
- Theme: `baller_app/lib/design_system/` · legacy `baller_app/lib/theme/app_colors.dart` · `app_spacing.dart` · `app_sizes` — use `AppColors` / `AppSpacing`.

## Models (`baller_app/lib/models/`)

- Follow `Court.dart`: `final` fields, `factory Model.fromMap(Map<String, dynamic> map)`.
- Read snake_case DB keys (`lat`, `lng`, `has_markings`, `lights`, `surface`).
- Cast: `(map['lat'] as num).toDouble()`; booleans with `?? false` defaults.

## Data access

- Use `RepositoryProvider.courts` / `.profiles` / `.auth` — not new Supabase calls when `USE_LEGACY_SUPABASE=false`.
- Repositories return `Map<String, dynamic>` lists; map to models at call site: `Court.fromMap(e)`.

## Services (`baller_app/lib/services/`)

- `load_position.dart` — `LocationService.loadPosition()` only.
- `badword_filter.dart` — call `BadwordFilter.loadWords()` in `main.dart` before `runApp`.
